title: #92Noon! Florio/Sandelin/Leber/Talkers
description: Florio starts the show, and Mav Hockey forward Ryan Sandelin finishes the first hour, Ben Leber in studio most of the middle hour, with Twins Communications mogul Dustin Morse joining for another cold call....final hour talkers on Wild and NFL!
